  "description": [
    "LAUREL OUTLOOK Published every Wednesday at Laurel Montana by Joseph Gehrett Campbell Calvert Subscription 250 per annum in advance Entered as secondclass matter July 14 1909 at the postoffice at Laurel Mont under act of March 3 1879 1950 NATION AL EDITORIAL About You By SKIPPY It is with the dawning of the new year that men take an uiven tory of the year past and make resolutions for the year coming So ease yourself into your fatontej chair and we will try to take stock We have fifty years left of the twentieth century with which to contend We have a world torn with war and very tired of it and we have a new war on our hands We have the knowledge of what the world has done for a good centuries Therefore wei many should be able to avoid a few mistakes We have a more worldly viewpoint than ever before and the knowledge that we will anni NOTICE To past patrons of the Laurel Refrigeration Ser vice As of December 26 1950 I have retired from business in order to enter the U S Naval service Thank you for your past patronage D K BRICKMAN 4"
  ],
